= SDL_FreeSurface =

Free an RGB surface.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void SDL_FreeSurface(SDL_Surface * surface);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''surface'''
|the [[SDL_Surface]] to free.
|}

== Remarks ==

It is safe to pass NULL to this function.

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 3.0.0.

